{"tid":2438869,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"播被迫認罪影片、不公正報導香港示威　英通訊局裁罰CGTN中國環球電視網22.5萬英鎊","createTime":"2021-03-08T23:35:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T05:35:01.000Z","uid":204533,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ce3a12b2cf99ac10be6541e2b769d4dde993e940","tid":2438869,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T23:35:36.000Z","msg":"英國通訊管理局（Ofcom）周一（3/8）向中國中央電視台旗下「中國環球電視網」（CGTN）罰款共22.5萬英鎊（約880萬元台幣），並裁定香港異見人士提出的兩起投訴案成立。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">Ofcom因應英國私家偵探韓飛龍（Peter Humphrey）的投訴，向CGTN罰10萬英鎊（約391萬元台幣）。韓飛龍指CGTN在2013年播出他在中國被迫認罪的片段。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nOfcom指CGTN「理應知道韓飛龍是審訊前，在扣留他的人在場下認罪，有理由懷疑他是否真誠並在知情的情況下認罪」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">CGTN亦因為2019年5個有關香港示威的節目違反英國廣播條例的公正持平原則，被罰款12.5萬英鎊</span></strong>（約488萬元台幣）。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">Ofcom又裁定CGTN播放瑞典籍書商桂民海及英國駐香港領事館前僱員鄭文傑被迫認罪片段的投訴成立，CGTN將面臨更多罰款</span></strong>。Ofcom指CGTN未採取足夠措施，確保桂民海認罪片的處理手法「沒對桂先生不公平」，又指CGTN沒有尊重鄭文傑的隱私，亦沒有充分揭露或報導他認罪時的情況。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"50d3635de22748e0aec76a00c6b4432ccece3942","tid":2438869,"uid":204533,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T23:36:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210309/OBOBMNPQVRBTHHKAWDVVKIKT7Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210309%2FOBOBMNPQVRBTHHKAWDVVKIKT7Q%2F&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1Rv0YzBSotcsoJ75UENuGtOl4%3D&h=a3b9da9c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210309%2FOBOBMNPQVRBTHHKAWDVVKIKT7Q%2F&h=0c672bd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210309/OBOBMNPQVRBTHHKAWDVVKIKT7Q/</a>"},{"pid":"b77e55c6d07deb6e9202ca6dd42765fa71bea29f","tid":2438869,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T23:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac